## Integration with Related Properties

The property works together with these related properties:

```turtle
# The three core declaration properties work together:

# WHO declares (P70.24)
<declaration> gmn:P70_24_indicates_declarant <person> .

# WHAT is declared (P70.25)
<declaration> gmn:P70_25_indicates_declaration_subject <subject> .

# TO WHOM it is declared - optional (P70.22)
<declaration> gmn:P70_22_indicates_receiving_party <recipient> .
```

