## Expected Transformation Output

After transformation, the shortcut property should be converted to CIDOC-CRM:

### Before Transformation (Input)

```turtle
<http://example.org/declaration001> a gmn:E31_5_Declaration ;
    gmn:P70_24_indicates_declarant <http://example.org/person_marco> .
```

### After Transformation (Output)

```turtle
<http://example.org/declaration001> a gmn:E31_5_Declaration ;
    cidoc:P70_documents <http://example.org/declaration001/declaration> .

<http://example.org/declaration001/declaration> a cidoc:E7_Activity ;
    cidoc:P2_has_type <http://vocab.getty.edu/page/aat/300027623> ;
    cidoc:P14_carried_out_by <http://example.org/person_marco> .

<http://example.org/person_marco> a cidoc:E39_Actor .
```

