## AAT Reference

The declaration activity type uses Getty AAT:

```turtle
<http://vocab.getty.edu/page/aat/300027623> a cidoc:E55_Type ;
    rdfs:label "declaration"@en .
```

**AAT 300027623 Definition**: "Written or oral statements made, as under oath before a notary public, by one who has knowledge of facts"

